title: Cheese Stuffed Bacon Wrapped Hot Dogs
directions: Pre-heat oven to 400°F. Make a slit in all of the hot dogs and insert sliced cheese into the slits.
Wrap each hot dog in 2 slices of bacon, then secure bacon on each end with toothpicks.
Place hot dogs on top of a wire rack that's on top of a cookie sheet.
Season the hot dogs, and bake for 35-40 minutes.
